# Build output
**/bin
**/obj

# IDE / OS
**/.vs
**/.vscode
**/.idea
**/*.user
**/.DS_Store

# Tests (runtime image doesn't need them)
tests/

# Local-only files
**/secrets.json
**/.env*
**/appsettings.*.json
!**/appsettings.json

# Git + docs
.git/
.gitignore
docs/
**/*.md
session-*-kickoff.md

# Agent persona + bounds docs are first-party runtime inputs (ADR 0012) —
# carve them back into the build context so the API Dockerfile can COPY them.
!docs/agent-voice-and-persona.md
!docs/agent-bounds.md

# Coverage / artifacts
**/coverage*
**/TestResults/
